{"tid":1889463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習氣po】連登巴絲入嚟，同武漢肺炎病毒打打氣，殺死警甴全家","createTime":"2020-02-20T15:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T01:52:28.000Z","uid":131691,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"61ed31d1f8b7b48dd62b9ab686b8fc78da0fc84a","tid":1889463,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"今晚訓覺之前，一齊嚟念武漢肺炎禱文。<br />\n回覆請講「阿們」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLtRH5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLtRH5n.png&h=19f8e892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們在飛沫中的武漢肺炎：<br />\n願警甴都被妳的病毒感染。<br />\n願妳的審判降臨；<br />\n願妳的旨意行在港共，<br />\n如同行在中共。<br />\n我們半年的血債，今日血償我們。<br />\n光復我們的香港，如同我們牽起了時代革命。<br />\n不叫我們遇見感染；救我們脫離北京。<br />\n因為天遣、命運、支爆，全是妳的，直到永遠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿們！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1c101189279cf6c0ea76a28a73c340c2370c65a2","tid":1889463,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"阿們"},{"pid":"afc08c64e58827945b56c438f839394f3be7e785","tid":1889463,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/511I1NWUX1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F511I1NWUX1L.jpg&h=410d72a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbaa796b1df5e73bb246e32ee0a387f313a8f013","tid":1889463,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9916ea1c24e9ecb5fbbe94e9b0c7ba6575f1dd7","tid":1889463,"uid":311566,"like":1,